#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.read_odps_table.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.read\\_odps\\_table"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:1 of
msgid "Read data from a MaxCompute (ODPS) table into DataFrame."
msgstr "从 MaxCompute (ODPS) 表中读取数据到 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:3 of
msgid ""
"Supports specifying some columns as indexes. If not specified, RangeIndex"
" will be generated."
msgstr "支持将某些列指定为索引。如果未指定，将生成 RangeIndex。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:6 of
msgid "Name of the table to read from."
msgstr "要读取的表名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:8 of
msgid "Table partition or list of partitions to read from."
msgstr "要读取的表分区或分区列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:10 of
msgid ""
"Table columns to read from. You may also specify partition columns here. "
"If not specified, all table columns (or include partition columns if "
"`append_partitions` is True) will be included."
msgstr ""
"要读取的表列。您也可以在此处指定分区列。如果未指定，将包含所有表列（或者"
"如果 `append_partitions` 为 True，则包含分区列）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:14 of
msgid "Columns to be specified as indexes."
msgstr "指定为索引的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:16 of
msgid ""
"If True, will add all partition columns as selected columns when "
"`columns` is not specified,"
msgstr "如果为 True，当未指定 `columns` 时，将添加所有分区列作为选定列，"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:19 of
msgid ""
"Back-end data type applied to the resultant DataFrame (still "
"experimental)."
msgstr "应用于结果 DataFrame 的后端数据类型（仍处于实验阶段）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:21 of
msgid ""
"Filter expression to apply when reading data.  - **String format**: SQL "
"WHERE clause passed directly to StorageAPI.  - **List format**: Nested "
"list of tuples.    Format: Inner lists are ANDed, outer lists are ORed."
"   Example: ``[[('col1', '==', 'value'), ('col2', '>', 10)]]``  Supported"
" operators: ``==``, ``!=``, ``<``, ``>``, ``<=``, ``>=``, ``in``, ``not "
"in``.  .. note::     Complete filtering is not guaranteed for this "
"argument given     implementation."
msgstr ""
"读取数据时应用的过滤表达式。  - **字符串格式**: 直接传递给 StorageAPI 的 "
"SQL WHERE 子句。  - **列表格式**: 嵌套的元组列表。    格式: 内部列表使用 "
"AND 连接，外部列表使用 OR 连接。   示例: ``[[('col1', '==', 'value'), ('"
"col2', '>', 10)]]``  支持的操作符: ``==``, ``!=``, ``<``, ``>``, ``<=``, "
"``>=``, ``in``, ``not in``。  .. note::     给定实现，不能保证此参数的"
"完整过滤功能。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:21 of
msgid "Filter expression to apply when reading data."
msgstr "读取数据时应用的过滤表达式。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:23 of
msgid "**String format**: SQL WHERE clause passed directly to StorageAPI."
msgstr "**字符串格式**：直接传递给 StorageAPI 的 SQL WHERE 子句。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:25 of
msgid "**List format**: Nested list of tuples."
msgstr "**列表格式**：嵌套的元组列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:27 of
msgid ""
"Format: Inner lists are ANDed, outer lists are ORed. Example: "
"``[[('col1', '==', 'value'), ('col2', '>', 10)]]``"
msgstr ""
"格式：内部列表使用 AND 连接，外部列表使用 OR 连接。示例：``[[('col1', '=="
"', 'value'), ('col2', '>', 10)]]``"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:30 of
msgid ""
"Supported operators: ``==``, ``!=``, ``<``, ``>``, ``<=``, ``>=``, "
"``in``, ``not in``."
msgstr ""
"支持的操作符：``==``, ``!=``, ``<``, ``>``, ``<=``, ``>=``, ``in``, ``not"
" in``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:33 of
msgid ""
"Complete filtering is not guaranteed for this argument given "
"implementation."
msgstr "由于实现原因，不能保证此参数的完整过滤功能。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:37 of
msgid "**result** -- DataFrame read from MaxCompute (ODPS) table"
msgstr "**result** -- 从 MaxCompute (ODPS) 表中读取的 DataFrame"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:41 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:42 of
msgid ""
"Before using `read_odps_table`, you need to create an ODPS entry whose "
"parameters will be stored globally in current process."
msgstr ""
"在使用 `read_odps_table` 之前，您需要创建一个 ODPS 条目，其参数将在当前"
"进程中全局存储。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:50 of
msgid "Simply read a table by name."
msgstr "简单地按名称读取表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:54 of
msgid "Read table by partition (or partitions)."
msgstr "按分区（或多个分区）读取表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:61 of
msgid "Read with column selection."
msgstr "带列选择的读取。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:65 of
msgid "Read with columns as index."
msgstr "将列作为索引进行读取。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.datasource.read_odps_table.read_odps_table:72 of
msgid ""
"Read with filter condition. Note that complete filtering is not "
"guaranteed."
msgstr "带过滤条件的读取。注意不能保证完整的过滤功能。"

